{"tid":88873,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"便秘求救","createTime":"2017-01-21T03:05:16.000Z","updateTime":"2017-01-21T14:52:12.000Z","uid":16886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"9f23eeb34167283d03219064b99d3ecdeeb438e4","tid":88873,"uid":16886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-21T03:05:16.000Z","msg":"是咁的<br />\n早星期開始就有便秘問題出現<br />\n要好大力先去屙得出<br />\n仲要一粒粒咁<br />\nD屎仲要未消化哂<br />\n仲見到食過嘅食物<br />\n咁就去左睇醫生<br />\n咁佢又話我冇事<br />\n可能係佢睇唔出<br />\n之後e幾日已經食左火龍果<br />\n但都係有便秘問題<br />\n雖然每朝都有屙<br />\n但都係要用力先出到<br />\n想問下點解會咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我係咪有咩病"},{"pid":"35ab3052febf4eda0bf4e1ad2f1b65c1ff984964","tid":88873,"uid":16886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-21T03:13:59.000Z","msg":"E幾日已經戒左口<br />\n食好多粥同菜"},{"pid":"74fc32b9b22bdedbb8d61e11821339d90daf962e","tid":88873,"uid":57276,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-21T03:41:29.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>E幾日已經戒左口<br />\n食好多粥同菜</blockquote><br />\n試下食All Bran,不過好難食下<br />\n菜要食啲深綠色嘅，<br />\n娃娃菜椰菜嗰啲水份多纖維相對少<br />\n同埋飲多啲水，唔夠水都會屙粒粒屎"},{"pid":"1dc26616ab002d0c2dd993f2c479d65d5b3c2968","tid":88873,"uid":32314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-21T04:08:29.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"b4e1c9930dc2b2bbbecc108405a8e36850b57979","tid":88873,"uid":16886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-21T11:23:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>E幾日已經戒左口<br />\n食好多粥同菜</blockquote><br />\n試下食All Bran,不過好難食下<br />\n菜要食啲深綠色嘅，<br />\n娃娃菜椰菜嗰啲水份多纖維相對少<br />\n同埋飲多啲水，唔夠水都會屙粒粒屎</blockquote><br />\n我已經成日飲水<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e829be1b65c27e6d90ac95f02f1e05957d91b6bc","tid":88873,"uid":40308,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-21T11:32:51.000Z","msg":"去藥才舖買決明子沖茶飲<br />\n<br />\n決明子的清腸通便，緩解便秘的功效也是非常的顯著的，對經常便秘，能使排便順暢而不稀薄，也無腹痛等不適之症，慢性便秘患者，常服無流弊。<br />\n原文網址：<a href=\"https://read01.com/JxnnQ5.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fread01.com%2FJxnnQ5.html&d=j9tBPyUSi%2BxbPICQ9qKiS2N6obqfy%2FNc7jg2IsrTbnE%3D&h=f502e8e2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://read01.com/JxnnQ5.html</a>"},{"pid":"5e466c332877c69b5cf3dd6e2dd2a28909db119e","tid":88873,"uid":16886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-21T14:52:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>去藥才舖買決明子沖茶飲<br />\n<br />\n決明子的清腸通便，緩解便秘的功效也是非常的顯著的，對經常便秘，能使排便順暢而不稀薄，也無腹痛等不適之症，慢性便秘患者，常服無流弊。<br />\n原文網址：<a href=\"https://read01.com/JxnnQ5.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fread01.com%2FJxnnQ5.html&d=j9tBPyUSi%2BxbPICQ9qKiS2N6obqfy%2FNc7jg2IsrTbnE%3D&h=f502e8e2\" target=\"_blank\">https://read01.com/JxnnQ5.html</a></blockquote><br />\n唔該巴打 我聽日去試下<br />\n仲有冇其他方法"}]}